analysis: The documents relate to land management and specifically address the withdrawal or revocation of withdrawal of public lands for resurvey in Wyoming, Colorado, and New Mexico. The documents cite the Act of June 25, 1910, and the Act of August 24, 1912. Some orders establish withdrawals pending resurvey, while others revoke previous withdrawal orders after the resurvey plat has been filed.
title: Land Resurvey Modifications
